<h2 id="general">General</h2>

<h3 id="purpose">Purpose</h3>

<p>Provide Quality Control (QC) guidelines for fault identification and rectification, and quality evaluations</p>

<h3 id="scope">Scope</h3>

<p>This Quality Control Procedure applies to all personnel performing sensor development, assembly and validation at FloodNet.</p>

<h2>Quality Requirements</h2>

<p>The following are the quality requirements of the Flood Sensor:</p>

