      <td>1.  The sensor Hardware shall be functional and tested before moving onto the software stage</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: left">Weatherproofed Sensor</td>
      <td>1. The sensor and itâ€™s housing shall be checked for any defects or potential damage that might cause failure in waterproofing</td>
